name: QuickVisits
0:
”Alexa, ask quick visits how many visitors”
”Alexa, tell quick visits to check how many visits”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: quick visits
des: Alexa app that checks how many people viewed my resume on my website. It does this by simply calling the DynamoDB API that holds a counter for how many visits I have. Invoking this skill is also considered a visit and will increment said counter as well.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
